@using Feirb.Web.Components.UI

<Heading Level="HeadingLevel.Large" Icon="palette2">Design Fundamentals</Heading>

<Card Class="mb-3 p-4">
    <Heading Level="HeadingLevel.Small">Theme</Heading>
    <p>Feirb uses the <strong class="showcase-color-name">Electric Iris</strong> theme — a modern, soft light UI with subtle color accents, rounded surfaces, and generous spacing. No neon or glow effects; colors are flat. Pure black is avoided in favor of a deep blue-gray neutral.</p>
</Card>

<Card Class="mb-3 p-4">
    <Heading Level="HeadingLevel.Small">Color Palette</Heading>
    <div class="showcase-color-grid">
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #b6004f;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">Primary</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#b6004f --bs-primary</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">CTAs, active states, links</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #ff7195;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">Primary Container</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#ff7195 --feirb-primary-container</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Selection highlights, hover tints</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #006852;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">Secondary</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#006852 --bs-secondary</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Secondary actions, success indicators</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #FFE04A;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">Warning</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#FFE04A --bs-warning</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Warnings, tags, highlights</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #b31b25;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">Error</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#b31b25 --feirb-error</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Danger actions, validation errors</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #2d2d43;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">On Surface</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#2d2d43 --feirb-on-surface</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Body text, headings</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #5a5972;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">On Surface Variant</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#5a5972 --feirb-on-surface-variant</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Subtitles, secondary text</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #f8f5ff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">Background</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#f8f5ff --bs-body-bg</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Page background (light lavender)</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-color-item">
            <div class="showcase-color-swatch" style="background-color: #e8e5ff;"></div>
            <div class="showcase-color-info">
                <strong class="showcase-color-name">Surface Container</strong>
                <code class="showcase-color-token">#e8e5ff --feirb-surface-container</code>
                <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Hover backgrounds, input fills</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Card>

<Card Class="mb-3 p-4">
    <Heading Level="HeadingLevel.Small">Typography</Heading>
    <p>Primary font is <strong class="showcase-color-name">Inter</strong> with fallbacks to Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, and Arial.</p>
    <table class="table table-sm">
        <thead><tr><th>Element</th><th>Size</th><th>Weight</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>Heading Large (h1)</td><td>1.75rem</td><td>700</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Heading Medium (h2)</td><td>1.25rem</td><td>700</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Heading Small (h3)</td><td>1rem</td><td>700</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Body text</td><td>1rem (browser default)</td><td>400</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Subtitle / secondary</td><td>0.875rem</td><td>400</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Nav section labels</td><td>0.625rem uppercase</td><td>600</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</Card>

<Card Class="mb-3 p-4">
    <Heading Level="HeadingLevel.Small">Surfaces and Elevation</Heading>
    <table class="table table-sm">
        <thead><tr><th>Token</th><th>Value</th><th>Usage</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>Border radius</td><td><code>1rem</code> (16px)</td><td>Cards, modals</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Border radius (lg)</td><td><code>1.5rem</code> (24px)</td><td>Large containers</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Input radius</td><td><code>0.75rem</code> (12px)</td><td>Form controls</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Button radius</td><td><code>9999px</code></td><td>Pill-shaped buttons</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Shadow</td><td><code>0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)</code></td><td>Cards, primary buttons</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="mt-3 mb-0"><strong class="showcase-color-name">Layering:</strong> Base background → Raised cards (white, shadow) → Interactive elements (accent colors)</p>
</Card>

<Card Class="p-4">
    <Heading Level="HeadingLevel.Small">Icons</Heading>
    <p class="mb-2">All icons use <strong class="showcase-color-name">Bootstrap Icons</strong> (<code>bi-*</code>). Never use Google Material Symbols or other icon sets.</p>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-4">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
            <Icon Name="gear" Size="IconSize.Small" />
            <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Small (0.875rem)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
            <Icon Name="gear" />
            <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Default (1.25rem)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
            <Icon Name="gear" Size="IconSize.Large" />
            <span class="showcase-color-usage text-muted">Large (2rem)</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</Card>
